# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Real-time email verifier console (landing "Verify Any Email in Real-Time")
# The /api/verify route proxies the backend's PUBLIC validator
# (POST /api/public/validate-email) — the SAME endpoint the production
# landing page uses — so verdicts match targetpulse.net exactly.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL of the Express backend (no trailing slash).
# Local dev: http://localhost:5050   Prod: your Railway backend URL.
# (Same value as NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL used elsewhere; either is read.)
BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:5050
